\begin{abstract}
Solar power is a more environmentally friendly source of power than other traditionaly sources such as fossil fuels. In this study we looked into the potential for customers to save money by converting their homes to solar power. Specifically, we looked at the payment history of a single customer before and after converting to solar power, and used a first order autoregressive model to assess how much he was saving on his monthly power bill and how long it would take him to recover the intial cost of converting to solar power.
\end{abstract}

\section{Introduction}
% Does the report sufficiently describe the background of the problem?

% Solar power is an environmentally friendly alternative to fossil fuels. Additionally, solar
% customers can save money by installing solar panels on their home to generate their own power
% rather than relying on power from local power companies. The SolarSavings dataset contains
% monthly power bills to a customer both on and off solar power. The sales company would like
% to know (i) how much money per month, on average, does this customer save by converting to
% power and (ii) the projected time at which the customer will recoup the $15,000 cost of the solar
% equipment based on the projected monthly savings.

Solar power is a more environmentally friendly source of power than other traditionaly sources such as fossil fuels. Individuals that convert their homes to solar power can also often save money by generating their own power rather then constantly having to depend on power companies. Using the payment history of a single customer's power bills before and after having switched to solar power, we intend to explore a few questions that would be of particular interest to a solar power sales company. We will assess the average monthly savings of a customer who has converted to solar power, and how long it will take on average for a customer to recover the recover the initial \$8000 cost of converting to solar power. With answers to these questions, solar power sales companies can help their customers to better understand the benefits of switching to solar power. This will help the sales company to increase its profits, and contribute to on overall cleaner environment. 


\section{Data}
\label{data}
